'''Cosmoprof''' is a series of beauty and [[cosmetics]] [[trade show]]s that occur in locations around the world.<ref name=Sheng>{{cite news|last=Sheng|first=Ellen|title=Cosmoprof Asia: All Eyes Turn To China|newspaper=WWD: Women's Wear Daily|date=2012-12-28}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|title=COSMOPROF WORLDWIDE BOLOGNA|url=http://www.cosmoprof.com/trade-show/who-we-are/|publisher=SoGeCos SpA|accessdate=5 February 2013}}</ref> The flagship event in [[Bologna]] has been in existence since 1967<ref name=BeautyNews>{{cite news|title=Cosmoprof organizers increase investments|url=http://www.premiumbeautynews.com/en/cosmoprof-organizers-increase,4985|accessdate=5 February 2013|newspaper=Premium Beauty News|date=20 January 2013}}</ref> and draws 2,300 exhibitors from seventy countries and more than 170,000 visitors.<ref name=SundayTimes>{{cite news|title=US Embassy to support firms to visit Cosmoprof trade show in Bologna|url=http://www.timesofmalta.com/articles/view/20130203/business-news/US-Embassy-to-support-firms-to-visit-Cosmoprof-trade-show-in-Bologna.455954|accessdate=5 February 2013|newspaper=The Sunday Times|date=February 3, 2013}}</ref>
== Flagship Event in Bologna == It generally happens in the middle of March, along Cosmopack, a packaging cosmetic trade show. All the cosmetics specialities are represented within more than 20 halls: [[Makeup]], [[Hair care|haircare]], [[Skin care|skincare]], etc.
There are 2 special halls: "Country Pavilion", that gathers rock star companies from every countries, and "Prime", that gathers rising stars from all the industry.
