{{Infobox settlement | name = Sudirman Central Business District | native_name = | native_name_lang = | other_name = SCBD | nickname = | settlement_type = [[Central business district#Indonesia|Business district]] | image_skyline =SCBD, Jakarta.jpg | image_alt = | image_caption = Sudirman Central Business District skyline | coordinates = {{coord|-6.2262|106.8098|display=inline}} | subdivision_type = Country | subdivision_name = {{flag|Indonesia}} | subdivision_type1 = City | subdivision_name1 =[[South Jakarta]] | subdivision_type2 = Metro | subdivision_name2 = [[Jakarta]] | established_title = <!-- Established --> | established_date = | founder = | named_for = [[Sudirman]] | government_type = | governing_body = | unit_pref = Metric | area_footnotes = | area_rank = | area_total_km2 = 0.45 | elevation_footnotes = | elevation_m = | population_total = | population_as_of = | population_rank = | population_density_km2 = | population_demonym = | population_footnotes = | demographics_type1 = Languages | demographics1_title1 = Official | demographics1_info1 = [[Indonesian Language|Indonesian]] & [[English language|English]] | timezone1 = [[Time in Indonesia|WIB]] | utc_offset1 = +07:00 | area_code_type = | area_code = | blank1_name_sec1 = | blank1_info_sec1 = | postal_code_type = | postal_code = 12190 | registration_plate = | website = http://scbd.com/ | footnotes = }} '''Sudirman Central Business District''' or '''SCBD''' is a business district with an integrated mixed use development concept, located in [[South Jakarta]], [[Indonesia]], consisting of condominiums, office buildings, hotels, shopping and entertainment centers. The total area of SCBD is about 45 hectare, which is again divided into 25 lots. About 13 hectares of the district are used to develop road network and landscaping.<ref>{{cite web|url=http://scbd.com/|title=SCBD}}</ref> SCBD is located within [[Golden Triangle of Jakarta]]. There are seven entry and exit points from SCBD to different avenues of Jakarta. Most of the office buildings in the district are connected by underground pedestrian links. ==Important buildings== [[File:SCBD Jakarta.jpg|thumb|SCBD from street level]] The 2nd tallest building in Indonesia, [[Treasury Tower]] is located in the district at present. [[Jakarta Signature Tower]], which is under construction, once completed it will be the 5th tallest building in the world, is located in the district.<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.thejakartapost.com/news/2012/01/11/scbd-get-world-s-5th-tallest-building.html|title=SCBD to get world’s 5th tallest building}}</ref>
Important buildings in the districts are: {{div col|colwidth=20em}} *[[Treasury Tower]] *[[Pacific Place Jakarta]] *[[Equity Tower]] *[[The Energy]] *[[District 8 Jakarta|District 8]] *[[Indonesia Stock Exchange]] *[[Alila Hotels and Resorts|Alila SCBD]] *[[PCPD Tower]] *[[Sequis Centre Tower]] *SCBD Suites *Artha Graha *Capital Residence *Kusuma Chandra *JAK TV Building {{div col end}}
==Transportation== SCBD is served by [[TransJakarta]] [[TransJakarta Corridors|Corridor-1]]. Other bus service providers such as [[Kopaja]], [[:id:Mayasari Bakti|Mayasari Bakti]] and APTB buses also have routes, those passes through main avenues surrounding the district and connect the district with other parts of the city. SCBD will be integrated with a station of [[Jakarta MRT]] on [[Jalan Jenderal Sudirman]]. During business hours free shuttle buses are available to move within the district at 8-10 minutes interval.
